Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.71,0:00:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玄黄端现 太极混沌如鸡蛋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln the beginning, there was darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着轰的一声\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生了无限膨胀的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在所见超乎我们的想象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, see further than we've ever imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越了客观认知极限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond the limits of our existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所知的万物 时间 空间 物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Everything that we know, time, space, and matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都将在劫难逃\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依赖阳光生存的所有生命都将很快灭绝\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Any life that depends on sunlight will rapidly go extinct...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为维系生命的能源越发稀少\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as there are fewer sources of life-providing energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是炼狱里的世界末日\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Whether by the Armageddon of an inferno...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是困于冰魔之爪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or in the grip of an icy executioner...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙本身将命丧冻结 所有生命无一幸免\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The universe itselfwill freeze to death and all life with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃至深太空里无形的力量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Or even by an unseen force from the depths of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:00:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确确实实 每一个粒子 每一个原子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And literally every particle, every atom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙间的每一个结构都将爆发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}every structure in the universe would explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.93,0:01:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐稳了 马上进入[宇宙末日]了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Beware, here comes the "CosmicApocalypse."
