Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[历史频道] 第二季 第十八集 宇宙末日\N[History Channel] The UniverseⅡ 18of19 Cosmic.Apocalypse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公元200亿年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The year is 20 billion A.D...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙出现了严重的错误\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and there is something gravely wrong with the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从爆炸诞生以来 宇宙一直在膨胀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ever since its explosive birth, the universe has been expanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断长大 永不见底\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}growing ceaselessly into an infinite unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 在遥远未来的一天\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}However, on this day in the distant future...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仰望星空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}looking up at the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四面八方的星系发生了逆转\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}galaxies from all directions have reversed course...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加速奔向我们的银河系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and are speeding towards our own Milky Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灾难带来万世之劫\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The catastrophic implication is fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙在塌缩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The universe is collapsing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所知的万物将终结于斯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and everything we know will cease to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命在劫难逃了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Life is doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看到其它星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When we look at other galaxies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到它们在磕磕碰碰中直奔我们而来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we'll see them coming in toward us on a collision course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.33,0:02:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然 我们看到行星从四面八方奔来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All of a sudden, we see stars coming at us from all directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有星系开始碰撞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All the galaxies will start colliding...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面的恒星碰撞在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the stars within them will get crunched together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恒星相撞 行星相撞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The stars will collide, the planets will collide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行星将被恒星吞没\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Planets will get swallowed by stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然之间 温度升高了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All of a sudden, temperatures begin to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然之间 海洋沸腾了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All of a sudden, the oceans boil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然之间 山体熔化了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All of a sudden, the mountains will melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 天哪 简直乱套了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, man, it's going to be chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片混乱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's going to be pandemonium.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙的温度开始飙升了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the universe itself begins to reach blistering temperatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的智能生命早已丧命 因为我们全都命葬火海了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All intelligent life must die because we'll all be incinerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙在巨响中终结于一个火球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The universe ends with a bang, in a cosmic fireball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是启示录的景象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is the vision of the Apocalypse...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源自大塌缩理论\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}according to a theory known as the Big Crunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大塌缩脚本里的情景\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What's happening with the Big Crunch scenario...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是宇宙间所有的物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is that all of the matter in the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的能量 星系 恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and all the energy, the galaxies, the stars in them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将通通移回原位\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are all moving back towards each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙塌缩了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the universe is shrinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物体将越靠越近\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Things are getting closer and closer together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的宇宙 刚好相反 在膨胀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our universe right now, on the other hand, is expanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都在增加空间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Each day, there is more and more space...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星系分得越来越开\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as galaxies get further and further apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大塌缩期间的情况刚好相反\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The opposite happens during the Big Crunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物体之间的空间在压缩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The space between things is shrinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像这廊道里挤满了人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that's rather like filling up this hallwaywith people...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人越来越多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and there are more and more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们之间的空间变得越来越小\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The space between them, then, is getting smaller and smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们摩肩接踵\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They bump into each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们努力相互闪避\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they're trying to dodge out of each other"s way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 所有的东西都在升温 能量越来越大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and so everything is heating up. and getting more and more energetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越多的情况发生在了这个不大的空间里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as more and more things happen in this small space.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的情况就发生在大塌缩的情景中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Exactly the same thing would happen in the Big Crunch scenario...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:04:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,构成万物的各种粒子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where various particles that make everything up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此相碰越发频繁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are bumping into each other more frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星系与恒星在相互靠近时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The galaxies and the stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始碰撞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as they're getting closer to each other...start distorting each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因而整个开始升温\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and so the whole thing's beginning to heat up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像人满为患的房间里温度会升高一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just like a crowded room would heat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个过程会持续下去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The process continues...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着宇宙的温度变得越来越高\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with the temperature of the universe getting higher and higher...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃至原子本身开始土崩瓦解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to the point that the atoms themselves begin to fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终 我们广袤的宇宙会垮塌成一个微点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Finally, ourvast universe collapses...into a microscopic point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将终结于物质汤羹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We'll end up with this soup of matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其作料是基本粒子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which is made offundamental particles...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在高能 高温下不停地搅和\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which are milling around at high energy, high temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所知的生命一网打尽\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Life as we know it has no escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 宇宙或许最终不会点燃熊熊的地狱之火\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}However, the universe may not ultimately ignite...into an all-consuming hellfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于世界末日有两种剧基本的说法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are two basic paradigms for the end ofthe world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个 宇宙将终结于大火\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}First, the universe is going to end in fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是基督教的世界末日理论\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's the Christian theory ofArmageddon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大火和硫磺 依次出现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}fire and brimstone and the second coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而挪威人也有自己的传说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the Norse also had their legends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们有毁灭之日的传说 诸神之黄昏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They had the legend of Ragnarok, Twilight ofthe Gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称 会有可怕的暴风雪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where there would be this monstrous snowstorm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞噬整个宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that would engulf the entire universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天堂里会有一场恶战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There would be this great battle in heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至奥丁神(战神) 托尔神(雷神)以及各路神灵\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and even Odin and even Thor and all the great gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会逐个慢慢死去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would slowly die one by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都将死于大冻结\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and we would all die in a great freeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至连神灵都通通死翘翘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when even the gods themselves are frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管大塌缩符合基督教版本的世界末日\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Whereas the Big Crunch fits the Christian vision of the end of days...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而科学界也有不同的理论\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}science also has a different theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即有可能是终结于冰冻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that it may instead all end in ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终 取决于宇宙膨胀的势头\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ultimately, it depends on whether the momentum...of the expansion of the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否克服引起塌缩的引力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}can overcome the collapsing attraction of gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象一下 球拍与球接触的瞬间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lmagine that the moment of contact between bat and ball...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是大爆炸的初始爆发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the initial explosion ofthe Big Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有东西被喷发出去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Everything's being thrown outward...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是 它是会自己重新塌缩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the issue is, will it re-collapse upon itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是会继续膨胀呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}orwill it continue to expand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两种可能性同时存在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And those two possibilities are very similar...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦你将球打出去后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to what happens when you launch a ball into the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我往高处打 重力相对击打瞬间的力量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf l launch it upwards, and if gravity is strong enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足够大话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}compared to how much energy l put into that initial launch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重力就会将球拉回来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it'll pull it back down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就像宇宙膨胀一段时间后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that's like the universe expanding out for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又折腾回来了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then crunching back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过大塌缩并不一定是一切的终结\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the Big Crunch doesn't have to be the end of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果宇宙塌缩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf the universe collapses...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能随之而来的是又一次大爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}what might subsequently follow is another Big Bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一轮膨胀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}another expansion event...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能膨胀一段时间后再次塌缩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that might expand for a while and then re-collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你可以想象那种可能性\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you can imagine the possibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上宇宙就是在循环\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that actually the universe isjust cyclic...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,膨胀 收缩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and so it expands...and then contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一次弹跳都是又一次大爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Each bounce is another Big Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而是否就不存在足够的引力来掌控宇宙呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But what if there isn't enough gravity to rein in the universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用足够的力道将其击打出去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l launch it upwards with enough energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就完全逃逸了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that it completely escapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙间没有足够的质量让其重新塌缩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's not enough mass in the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样它就会一路膨胀下去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to make it re-collapse, and so it continues to expand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终 尽管这种膨胀会放缓脚步\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Eventually, though this expansion ought to slow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是骇人的是 科学观察揭示的是迥然不同的情况\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}shockingly, scientific observations reveal something completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,膨胀正变得越来越快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's getting faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙貌似脱缰之马\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The universe seems to be careening out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,膨胀在加速 它在再次发飙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This expansion is accelerating. lt's kicking in once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正经历着暴涨式扩张\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We are undergoing an inflationary expansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们现在知道的宇宙正在膨胀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So the universe we now know is expanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其额外的加速超乎你的想象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with this extra acceleration...that is beyond what you would have thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全要归咎于初始爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}wasjust due to the initial explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不光是球逃逸了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Not only does the ball escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好像是球上装了一个小火箭引擎\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but it's as though a little rocket engine was on the ball...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在加速远离地球 越来越快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it accelerates away from the Earth even faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种可能性真是有点始料未及的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is a possibility that was somewhat unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙空间的容量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The volume of space in the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看似注定增大无止境\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}seems destined to increase forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就意味着遥远的星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What this means is that distant galaxies...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会快速远离我们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are going to go zooming away from us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终会离开视野\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and will eventually become invisible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它们会远到难以发现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because they'll be too far away to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到星系彼此快速远离\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And without seeing galaxies rushing away from each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来的文明将会失去所有的历史感\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}future civilizations will lose all sense of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不会知道曾经有过大爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They won't know that there was ever a Big Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:09:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 你会觉得宇宙间唯一的结构就是银河系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you will think that the only structure...within the universe is the Milky Way galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙的其余部分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that the rest of the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是一片空白 没有星星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is effectively empty, devoid of stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个科学理论主张\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Another scientific theory proposes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种膨胀会越发加快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that this expansion will balloon even faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦出现这种情况 残酷的末日就会降临我们的宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lfthis does happen, a violent end awaits our cosmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假设可恶的能量在单位时间里加大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Suppose the amount of repulsive energy...increases with time per unit volume.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终将会增强到引起星系团分崩离析\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt'll eventually grow strong enough...to cause clusters of galaxies to get ripped apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随后星系本身也将土崩瓦解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then galaxies themselves will get ripped apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恒星将开始相互远离\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The stars will start flying away from one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再靠引力彼此拴住\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}no longer held together by gravity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是行星系 如我们的太阳系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then planetary systems like our solar system...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也将分崩离析\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will get ripped apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是恒星 行星都将分崩离析\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then stars and planets will get ripped apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是人类也将分崩离析\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then humans will get ripped apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是构成我们的每个原子也将分崩离析\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then the very atoms ofwhich we are made will get ripped apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这被称为大撕裂 那真是毛骨悚然的情况\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's called the Big Rip, and it's a really scary possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:09:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过请别担心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们多数人并不认为会发生那样的情况\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Most of us don't think it's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使膨胀的速度永远不会到达那个临界点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But even ifthe rate of expansion never reaches this tipping point...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们宇宙的未来依然前程未卜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the future of our universe still isn't promising.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其温度会降低\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lts temperature decreases.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变得越来越冷 越来越暗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's getting colder and colder and darker and darker...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为微弱的星光将会照射更大的空间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because the feeble light emitted by stars...is going into a progressively larger volume...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因而宇宙将会变得极其寒冷 极其黑暗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so the universe is going to get really cold and really dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上是个阴森之地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Basically, a pretty gloomy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙本身 我们现在认为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The universe itself, we now believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会死于冰 而非死于火\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will die in ice, rather than fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为宇宙将会死于大冻结\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We think the universe will die in a great freeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像挪威传说预言的那样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just like the Norse legends foretell...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而非这个大塌缩里的世界末日\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}rather than this Armageddon of a Big Crunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果宇宙坚持目前的进程\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf the universe continues on its present course...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:11:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将注定有一个宇宙冰河时代 阳光将会熄灭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we're destined for a cosmic ice age where sunlight itself goes extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了公元100万亿年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By the year 100 trillion A.D...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一息尚存的人类文明\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the last remnants of human civilization...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能被迫蜗居在我们星系的这个偏远的黑暗角落里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}may be forced to settle here in this distant dark corner of our galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们蜷缩在最后尚在燃烧的恒星旁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They'll be huddled around the last burning star in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而悲哀的是 它很快也将寿终正寝\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but, sadly, it too will soon die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的银河系 取名来自明亮的星带\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our Milky Way, so named for its shimmering band of sparkling stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将面目全非\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will be unrecognizable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昏暗的恒星躯壳余火未尽的灰烬\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faint glowing embers of dark stellar husks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将成为曾经辉煌一时的夜景的残骸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will be all that remain...of what was once a brilliant night vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星体都是怎么啦？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What happened to all of the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么会遭遇如此悲惨的境况的呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How did we arrive at such a dismal scenario?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:12:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学判定随着我们宇宙膨胀和年长 它将会冷却\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Science decrees that as our universe expands and ages, it will cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可避免 我们知道其未来人生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lnevitably, the future for life as we know it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会变得越发充满敌意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will grow ever more hostile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们迈进的时代\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We are headed for a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会是有朝一日宇宙自身连同其中的生命通通被冻死\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when one day the universe itself will freeze to death and all life with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是法则\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that's a law.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们科学家研究宇宙的演化时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When we scientists look at the evolution of the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有批评者说 真是疯了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}some critics say, "That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们连预测明天的头条新闻都难以做到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"We can barely predict tomorrow's headlines...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里预言今后几十亿 上百亿年后的事情\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"and here you are predicting what's going to be happening..."billions and billions ofyears from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"How do you do it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在科学家考量未来的工具里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Among the tools available to scientists pondering the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有古老的热力学定律\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are the venerable laws of thermodynamics.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其第一定律称质量和能量的总值是守恒的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The first law says that total matter and energy are conserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换言之 你无法无中生有\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln otherwords, you can't get something for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有免费的午餐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's no free lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 结果就是一个系统里的物质和能量总量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So it turns out that the total amount of matter and energy in a system...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是既不能被创造也不能被毁灭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}can be neither created nor destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物质和能量可以改变形式\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The matter and energy can change forms...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以相互转换\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and they can turn into one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而总量不变\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but the total remains the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举个例子 在这张卷起的报纸里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, for example, in this rolled-up newspaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有大量的能量储存在报纸的化学键里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there's a lot of energy stored in the chemical bonds of the paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一旦我点燃报纸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but if l ignite the paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就可以激活这些化学键 开始破坏它们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l can activate those bonds, and l can start breaking them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以光和热的形式释放出能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that releases energy in the form of light and heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以看到和感觉到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which you can see and feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总能量依然没变\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The total energy content is still the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是它消散进了空间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but it's being dissipated out into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大量的微粒物质散发了 烟散发了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And a lot of particulate matter goes off as well and smoke goes off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果我将所有的烟雾 微粒物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but if l were to add up...all the smoke and the particulate matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,释放的所有能量以及所有东西加在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and all the energy that's given off and everything total...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就会得到和一开始完全相同的质量和能量的总量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I would get exactly the same amount...of mass and energy total as l had to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们只是改变了形式\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They simply changed forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果质量和能量的总和保持不变\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf the total amount of mass and energy remain constant...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这似乎就意味着宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}this seems to imply the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将永远具有能量 应该永续长存\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will always have energy and should last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是热力学第二定律打破了这种说法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the second law of thermodynamics...crushes this notion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热力学第二定律是最奇妙的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The second law of thermodynamics...is the most curious of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它说无序 即熵的总量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt says that total amount of disorder or entropy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在宇宙间总是在提高\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}always increases in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换言之 物体生锈 物体衰败\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln otherwords, things rust, things decay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物体老化 最终分化瓦解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}everything gets old and eventually falls apart and rots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某种意义上说 第二定律就是死刑执行令\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln some sense, the second law is a death warrant...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是宇宙的死刑执行令\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a death warrant for the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二定律声称无一能幸免\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The second law says all things must pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙间取之不尽的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The ever-present supply of energy in the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可避免的变得更加分散\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}inevitably becomes more dispersed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加无序 更加无用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}more chaotic, and more unusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上每一颗燃烧的星星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Each star burning in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这里的每一块木炭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just like each briquette of this charcoal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终有一天面对厄运\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}must one day face its fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这块木炭是燃料\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This piece of charcoal is fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大量的能量浓缩在这小小的木炭里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It has a lot of energy...concentrated into this small, little packet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自木炭里化学键的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That energy goes from being in the chemical bonds...of the charcoal briquette...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会以光和热的形式释放出来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to being liberated in the form of heat and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恒星上的情况一模一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, a star does a similar thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不是化学意义上的燃烧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt doesn't burn in a chemical sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是 恒星上烧的是核能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lnstead, in a star, it's nuclear energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原子核被压在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The nuclei of atoms are being forced together...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚合产生新的原子核\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}fusing them, creating new nuclei...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此过程中将部分物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and, in the process, transforming some of that matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部分质量转换成我们能看到 能感觉到的辐射能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}some of that mass, into the radiated energy that we see and we feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的进程还在宇宙中的活跃的恒星上继续\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the same process is going on...in all the active stars in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 随着这块木炭的燃烧 燃料正逐渐耗尽\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, as this charcoal is burning, the fuel is getting used up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:15:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以看得一清二楚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and you can actually see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其颜色正在变成灰\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's turning into a gray color.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在变成灰烬\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's turning into ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样道理 恒星在耗尽自己的燃料\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln a similarway, stars use up theirfuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们将氢聚合成氦 这样 随着时间的推移\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They fuse hydrogen into helium, and so, with time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氢燃料将变得越来越少\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there's less and less hydrogen to fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰烬中的能量很少\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the ashes have less energy content...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因而 要么难以燃烧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and, thus, are either harder to burn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么燃烧时释放很少的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or release less energy during the burning process.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们的太阳的最终结局\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is the eventual fate of our own Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着年长 它会膨胀和升温\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As it ages, it bloats and heats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球会烤成炸土豆片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Earth will be fried to a crisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海洋沸腾 动植物通通完蛋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oceans will boil away, all plants and animals will die...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩石气化\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}rocks will start vaporizing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太阳会发出强烈的阳光 剧烈的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because the Sun will be producing so much light, so much energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那对地球可谓是万世之劫\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That'll be a pretty gruesome death for the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纵观宇宙 太阳之类的恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All through the universe, stars that are like the Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都将面临我们太阳所面临的下场\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are going to be facing the same challenges...that our own starwill face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们在耗尽燃料 它们在膨胀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're running out offuel, they're swelling up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们在对围绕自己的行星制造麻烦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and they're causing problems for the planets that orbit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不难想象许多地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So it's not hard to imagine that there are many locations...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命曾经进化和繁育的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where life has evolved and flourished...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正在步入死亡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and is now being extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如所有的恒星遭遇熵的影响\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just as each star suffers the effects of entropy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙的其它地方也难逃厄运\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so, too, will the rest of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而恒星自然而然会通过散发光和热\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But stars naturally increase the entropy of the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来增加宇宙的熵\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by giving off light and heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这木炭燃烧的火\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just like this fire of burning charcoal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在自然而然地增加宇宙的熵一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}naturally increases the entropy of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下我们正处于宇宙的一个稳定期\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Right nowwe're kind of in a steady period in the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恒星诞生 度过星生 消亡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where stars are born, live out their lives, die...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下部分气体给下一代\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}give some of that gas back to the next generation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有了新一代的恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and you have another generation of stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:18:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过恒星形成的速度会随时间逐步减缓\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But that rate of star formation is gradually decreasing with time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着恒星的燃料的耗尽\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And as stars use up theirfuel and burn out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将没有足够的新恒星形成 来替代它们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there aren't enough new stars being formed to replace them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 此刻我们耗尽了形成新恒星的气体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the moment we run out of gas to make new stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这意味着 对于在册排队的每一颗死亡之星来说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it means for every dead star in the rolls, in the ranks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并没有替代之星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there's not a star to replace it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 那就是有朝一日的糟糕情况\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And so that's a bad situation to be in...the day that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 实际上 星系 恒星的巨大集合体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, effectively, galaxies, giant collections of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普遍会随着时间逐渐暗淡下去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are growing progressively dimmerwith time on average.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后 当宇宙到了100万亿岁以后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And, eventually, when the universe...is something like a hundred trillion years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将基本上不再有闪烁的星星了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there will be essentially no stars still shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙将变得极其寒冷 极其黑暗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The universe will be cold and dark indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何依赖阳光的生命将迅速灭绝\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Any life that depends on sunlight will rapidly go extinct...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为宇宙在衰老\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as the universe continues to age...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自母星的维持生命的能源也越来越少\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and as there are fewer and fewer sources of life-providing energy...from a host star.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:19:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能会觉得恒星个头最大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You might think the most massive stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,携带的燃料最多 持续的时间也会最长\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the ones with the most fuel, will last the longest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 恒星携带的燃料越多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln reality, the more fuel a star carries...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其燃烧的速度也越快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the faster it burns through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙中最后一抹阳光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The final rays of sunlight left in the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将来自所谓的红矮星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will come from stars known as red dwarfs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些微型恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These miniature stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,质量比我们太阳小10倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ten times less massive than our own sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温度会低数千度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}burn thousands of degrees cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红矮星非常吝啬自己的燃料消耗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Red dwarf stars are much more miserly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因而 尽管其一开始的燃料就不多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with theirfuel consumption...and so, even though they have less fuel to begin with...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 它们持续的时间比我们的太阳长得多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they last much, much longer than our Sun will last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,典型的红矮星可以存活万亿年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A typical red dwarf can live for as long as 14 trillion years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我们现在的宇宙年龄要长上1000倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's a thousand times longer than the current age of our universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是最终 这些吝啬的小太阳也免不了一死\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Eventually, though, even these stingy little suns...will begin to die off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以到了我们银河系几十万亿岁时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So when our Milky Way galaxy is tens of trillions ofyears old...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:20:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有少量的红矮星在那里苟延残喘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and there's only a few red dwarfs remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以想象一息尚存的文明\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you might imagine that any surviving civilizations...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会意识到末日的来临\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will realize that the end is nigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会簇拥在这几个能源周围\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and they will start crowding around these few sources of energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竭力掏空以求生存\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}trying to scrape out an existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红矮星可能是广袤 荒芜的宇宙中的生命绿洲\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Red dwarfs could be oases of life...in the vast, inhospitable desert of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 对于需要大量热和能量的行星来说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But for a planet to receive as much heat and energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从红矮星那里获得和地球从太阳获得的一样多的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from its red dwarf host as our Earth does from the Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就需要靠得很近\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it would need to orbit so closely...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其一年只相当于6个地球日\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that one full year would lastjust six Earth days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空要比地球这里的蓝天红上好多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The sky would be much more sort ofwhitish red...than our blue skies here on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为红矮星发出的蓝光少的可怜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because the red dwarf puts out so little blue light...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法看到我们这里看到的蓝天\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you wouldn't be able to have the kind of nice blue skies...that we have here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 宇宙间已经没有更热 更亮的东西了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}However, nothing left in the universe would be hotter or brighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们银河系终有一朝\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, there will be a time in our galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有几颗红矮星还在发光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when there'sjust a few red dwarfs still glowing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许就只有那么三两颗在眨着眼睛\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and maybejust then three and two and one as they blink out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪 当只有一颗红矮星的时候\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And, gosh, when there's one red dwarf left...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假设我呆在围绕着它的行星上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and suppose l'm on the planet circling it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想 噢 天哪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l'll think, "Man, oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙是个多么寂寞的地方啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}'what a lonely place the universe is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的未来惨不忍睹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"What a depressing future it holds."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一颗红矮星不复存在后又将如何呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What happens after the last red dwarf blinks out of existence?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,21世纪的地球生命生机勃勃\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Life in the 21st century on Earth thrives within a universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活在大爆炸以后 已经存在了140亿年的宇宙间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that has existed for about14 billion years...since the spark of the Big Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在宇宙的宏伟规划里 那简直就是弹指一挥间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But that's no time at all in the grand scheme of the cosmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是宇宙相对人的寿命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf the universe is comparable to a human life span...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:22:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还处于宇宙的襁褓期\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we are still in the infancy of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领悟过去以及未来的时光让人头大不已\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Getting a grasp of the time that has already elapsed...and the time span still to come can boggle the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了获得宇宙时间尺度的远景\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To gain a perspective of the vast time scales of the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们来把宇宙的140亿年历史\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}let's compress the roughly 14-billion-year history of the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,压缩成一个普通的日历\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}into one normal calendaryear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.55,0:22:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们会将其称为宇宙日历\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But we'll call this a cosmic calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样大爆炸发生在元旦 1月1日\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So the Big Bang occurred on NewYear's, January1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.93,0:22:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在日历牌上 我们银河系形成于1月末\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On that scale, our Milky Way galaxy formed near the end of January...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的太阳系大约形成于8月初\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and our solar system formed around the beginning ofAugust or so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年过去了三分之二\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about two-thirds of the way through the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命出现在8月晚些的某个时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Life formed sometime a little bit later in August...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.99,0:22:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过人类出现还不到一天时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but humans formed less than a day ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.91,0:22:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 在12月31日的某个时间 人类终于出现了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, on December 31st sometime, humans finally arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.41,0:23:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们同样可以展望未来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We can also look into the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就利用同一个宇宙日历的时间尺度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}on the same cosmic calendar time scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在来年的1月底\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Near the end of January of this coming year...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的地球变得相当不友好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}our Earth will become quite inhospitable.
