Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.43,0:23:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还有其它一些恒星 低质量的恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but there are some other stars, the low-mass stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会存活得很长 很长\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which will live for much, much longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活过这样的宇宙年1万岁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}up to10,000 of these cosmic years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那比整个宇宙历史长出了1万倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's 10,000 times longer than the entire history of the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.45,0:23:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后那些最长命的红矮星才会退出历史舞台\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}before these final longest-living red dwarf stars die off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么接下来是怎么个情形呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But then what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们讨论极其遥远的未来时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When we talk about the extremely distant future...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨论的是极大的时间跨度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we're talking about immense spans of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.17,0:23:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间以千万亿年计\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}time measured in quadrillions ofyears...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.59,0:23:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万万亿年计\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and septillions ofyears...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.30,0:23:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经变得不知所措了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it becomes so overwhelming...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.14,0:23:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要发展另外的概念来处理它了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that we need to evolve another concept to really deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.64,0:24:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们就提出了宇宙年代的概念\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So we came up with the idea of cosmological decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.44,0:24:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙年代 就是每一个年代\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A cosmological decade, each decade is ten times longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是先前从开始以来的整个时段的十倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than all the time that happened prior to the start ofthe decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.36,0:24:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理解它的一个方法就是它好比台阶\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And one way to think about this is that it's like a staircase.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.07,0:24:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非像原来的这个台阶\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Not an ordinary staircase like this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.16,0:24:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是每一级台阶都是前面台阶的10倍高\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but one in which each step is ten times higher...than the step before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.79,0:24:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你可以想象台阶一级一级往上增高\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you can imagine the staircase going up and up and up...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.88,0:24:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙年代就越来越增大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to higher and higher cosmological decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.76,0:24:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前 我们正处于宇宙10年代\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Right now, we're living in the tenth cosmological decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.64,0:24:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照这个尺度 宇宙10年代\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On this scale, the tenth cosmological decade...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.85,0:24:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是10倍于大爆炸以来9个年代的总和\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is ten times longer than the previous nine decades combined...that have passed since the Big Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.36,0:24:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙10年代的标志\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The hallmark of the tenth cosmological decade...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.74,0:24:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上就是恒星在夜空灿烂闪烁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the fact that stars are burning brightly in the night sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.87,0:25:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时行星的表面开始孕育生命和智能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and also that the planets are beginning to develop...life and intelligence on their surfaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.04,0:25:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙10年代另一个有趣的标志\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Another interesting hallmark of the tenth cosmological decade...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.17,0:25:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是宇宙的膨胀开始加速\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the beginning of the acceleration...of the expansion ofthe universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.72,0:25:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着我们的宇宙年代的延续\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As our cosmological decade continues...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.39,0:25:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的其它星系将淡出视野\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all of the other galaxies disappearfrom view...
