Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.98,0:25:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在星系里闪烁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}shining in the galaxy at any one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.24,0:25:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那将会是世界啊 行星啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that will be the last sort of gasp...of the kind of world, the kind of planets...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.16,0:25:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们熟悉的环境之类的最后的抽气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the kind of environments that are familiar to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.04,0:25:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着我们经过随后的若干个宇宙年代\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As we move through the succeeding cosmological decades...
