Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.73,0:26:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们实际上会看到天上点缀着死去的恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then we'd actually see that the sky is speckled with dead stars.
