Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.82,0:26:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是怪异的灰烬 毫无疑问\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's weird ashes, that's for sure.
