Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.95,0:29:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我们一旦进入退化时代\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, as we go into the Degenerate Era...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.33,0:29:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会看到有上千亿颗死亡之星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we'll have roughly a hundred billion dead stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.87,0:29:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一个巨大的椭圆体里相互环绕\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}orbiting each other in a giant elliptical configuration.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.21,0:29:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔 它们会相互作用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Occasionally, they'll interact with one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.80,0:29:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中会有被逐出星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and one will get flung out ofthe galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.63,0:29:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致星系丧失质量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}causing the galaxy to lose mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.89,0:29:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星系 从某种意义上说 将会慢慢地蒸发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The galaxy, in a sense, will evaporate slowly with time...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.47,0:29:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴随着这些东西的抛出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as these things are flung out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.98,0:29:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白矮星以及残留的星际物质会掉入黑洞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}White dwarfs and remaining galactic material...fall prey to black holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.65,0:29:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日积月累 结果会是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So gradually, with time, what will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.74,0:29:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星系拥有的物质越来越少\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the galaxy will have fewer and fewer objects in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.53,0:29:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越多的部分将会变成黑洞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and a greater and greater fraction of them will be black holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.50,0:29:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都逃不脱自宇宙衰老开始\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And whatever isn't seized...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.00,0:30:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就游走其中的无数黑洞的魔爪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by the millions of black holes roaming the universe...begins to decay with old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.46,0:30:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是另一个一般过程的例子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And this is another example of the general process...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.55,0:30:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此过程中 宇宙间的熵的总量有增无减\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by which the total amount of randomness increases in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.85,0:30:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热力学第二定律再次发挥了作用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The second law of thermodynamics is once again at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.10,0:30:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的结构 所有的恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And all the structures, all the stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.48,0:30:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上消失殆尽了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are basically evaporating into nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.65,0:30:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以到了宇宙年代40年代左右\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and so by about cosmological decade forty...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.57,0:30:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,构建行星 恒星的大部分物质将完全消失\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}most of the stuff that's been built...the planets and the stars, are all gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.82,0:30:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退化时期 已经持续了很长时间了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the Degenerate Era...which has stretched for huge amounts of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.99,0:30:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将告结束\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.83,0:30:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,障碍通通扫清\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}With nothing left in theirway...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.04,0:30:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑洞统治宇宙的地位固若金汤\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}black holes stand poised to rule the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.92,0:30:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可能就是宇宙残酷的未来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This may be the grim future ofthe cosmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.30,0:30:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行星衰败解体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The planets decay and dissolve...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.22,0:30:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗星际残骸散落膨胀的宇宙间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}dark galactic remnants scatter across a bloated universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.73,0:31:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至连光都成了模糊 遥远的回忆\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and even light isjust a faint, distant memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.40,0:31:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着我们穿越深邃的时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As we continue through the vast stretches of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.86,0:31:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,度量宇宙年代\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}measured in cosmological decades...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.24,0:31:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大的黑洞幸存了下来成为了我们曾经星光灿烂的夜空中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}massive black holes survive as the only recognizable features...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.33,0:31:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一能识别的特征\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of our once brilliant night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.41,0:31:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来到了宇宙年代60年代前后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're up to about cosmological decade sixty-something...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.33,0:31:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时你仰望夜空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and when you look out at the night sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.34,0:31:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它出奇的冷 出奇的黑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's incredibly cold, it's incredibly black...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.59,0:31:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有最微弱的电波噼啪作响\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and there's only the faintest crackle of radio waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.68,0:31:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引力辐射 回荡在空无一物的空中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and gravitational radiation, echoing through the empty skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.44,0:31:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了黑洞时期了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is the Black Hole Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.82,0:31:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙的持续膨胀使其元气大伤\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The continuous expansion of the universe has taken its toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.70,0:31:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极度寒冷消耗能量 减缓进程\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The unimaginable cold saps energy and constricts movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.53,0:31:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间本身好像已失去意义\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Time itself seems to lose meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.79,0:32:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了黑洞时期中期 甚至退化时期\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln the midst of the Black Hole Era, even the Degenerate Era...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.67,0:32:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛处在了大爆炸后的时间起点上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}looks like the first sliver of time after the Big Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.46,0:32:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种环境中 生命还有机会吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Does life have a chance in this environment?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.38,0:32:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类那时将不复存在 因为质子都不存在了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Humans won't exist at that time because protons won't exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.18,0:32:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是可以设想有些实体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but it's possible to imagine some kind of entity...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.06,0:32:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以极其缓慢的速度存活着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which is living at an extraordinarily slow rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.77,0:32:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果生活缓慢的足够\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf it lives slowly enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.65,0:32:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会出现奇怪的生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}perhaps strange life could emerge.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.40,0:32:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个念头要用上数万亿年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A thought would take trillions ofyears.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.70,0:32:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也许需要用上万亿年来决定午餐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt may take a trillion years for you to decide what to have for lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.66,0:32:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一切都极其缓慢 一切都近乎绝对零\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because everything is so slow, everything is near absolute zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.96,0:32:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑洞时期的爬行时间尺度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The creeping time scale ofthe Black Hole Era...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.13,0:32:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以比作植物的成长\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}can be compared to the growth ofvegetation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.22,0:32:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从人类的角度出发 有关分 小时 天\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}From a human perspective, involving minutes, hours, and days...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.56,0:33:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,植物的生命似乎是时间的冻结\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}plant life can seem frozen in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.85,0:33:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没什么发生似的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Absolutely nothing seems to be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.69,0:33:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它似乎完全没有生机 完全静止不动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt appears to be completely dead, completely static.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.69,0:33:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们一旦加快时钟 就会看到它的活动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But ifwe speed up the clock, then we see the activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.03,0:33:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,植物的生长\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The plant grows...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.20,0:33:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,植物活动叶子对阳光作出反应\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the plant moves its leaves in response to where the Sun is...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.12,0:33:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,植物在不断活动 不停地干活\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the plant is continuously in motion, it's continuously doing things...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.96,0:33:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是其生存的尺度 就是时帧要长于\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but that whole scale of existence is on a time frame that's longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.13,0:33:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们通常的体验\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than what our experience is used to dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.72,0:33:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑洞时期地盘之争发生在两个黑洞狭路相逢时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The real action in the Black Hole Era occurs...when two black holes meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.06,0:33:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管肉眼看不到这两个猛兽的碰撞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Although invisible to human eyes, a collision between these two beasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.07,0:33:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是会通过时空发出颤动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}sends a shudder through space-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.99,0:34:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事件可以想象成在一汪静水之间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This event can be imagined in a sheet of perfectly still, calm water.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.41,0:34:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像在静水中突然投下一块大石头\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's a bit like suddenly dropping a gigantic rock into that calm water...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.92,0:34:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散开一系列涟漪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}sending out a huge series of ripples...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.79,0:34:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在一小段时间里看到很多活动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and you have a lot of action for a little bit oftime...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.59,0:34:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而随后就消失了 涟漪消失了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but then that dissipates, the ripples die away...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.63,0:34:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又回到了平静如镜的水面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and you're back to that smooth, glass-like sheet ofwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.81,0:34:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过对于这些黑洞时期的霸王而言\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But even for these kings of the Black Hole Era...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.93,0:34:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间也正在消失\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}time is running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.23,0:34:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你或许会想 噢 它们会万寿无疆的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And you might think, "Oh, they'll last forever"...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.90,0:34:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是它们绝不会万寿无疆的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but even they don't last forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.11,0:34:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 它们会随着时间极其缓慢地消失的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because they evaporate very, very slowly with time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.07,0:34:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天宇宙间的黑洞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Black holes in today's universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.95,0:34:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着吞噬周围的物质而愈长愈大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}grow larger as they gobble up surrounding matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.37,0:34:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过到了最终 遥远的未来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But eventually, far in the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.92,0:34:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞噬的物质少的可怜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there'll be so little material to swallow...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.04,0:34:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消亡的速度将开始占上风\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that the evaporation rate will start dominating...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.88,0:34:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜过它们吞噬周围物质的速度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}over the rate at which they swallow material from their surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.84,0:35:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以消亡的速度将越来越快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So the evaporation rate proceeds more quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.97,0:35:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴随着宇宙越来越衰老\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when the universe is very, very old.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.14,0:35:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失中的黑洞是不会发出哀鸣的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}An evaporating black hole does not go out with a whimper...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.65,0:35:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像行星在临终前那样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like the planets do when they die...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.15,0:35:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是发出一声巨响\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but ratherwith a bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.40,0:35:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为 当其耗尽燃料时 行为有些不可理喻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's because it behaves counterintuitively...as it runs out offuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.20,0:35:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上有两种策略可供你选择\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's basically two strategies that you can adopt.
